{"tid":500168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又.....發現 iOS 11.2.1 訊息 App 仍有「emoji漏洞」","createTime":"2017-12-15T13:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T14:32:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c02c7ab44c0a6314403f02ffc3af762a48c9ffa5","tid":500168,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"這個漏洞與 emoji 有關，在訊息 App 打開新的對話介面，在第 1 個訊息輸入一個 emoji 然後送出，就會看到輸入的 emoji 不能在訊息 App 顯示之餘，上方的聯絡人清單以及退回訊息清單的按鈕也消失，要強制關閉訊息 App 進程才能重新顯示。<br />\n<br />\n這個「萬年漏洞」去到 11.1.2、iOS 11.2 和 iOS 11.2.1 也沒有解決，即使最近推出的 iOS 11.2.5 beta 1 版也沒有解決，並影響 iOS 裝置內所有 SMS 和 iMessage 訊息。<br />\n<br />\n早前 iOS 11.2.1 解決了多個漏洞，包括 HomeKit 漏洞、iPhone 相機自動變焦漏洞、iOS 自動修正漏洞以及寒冷天氣問題，這些問題是在早些星期出現，不令不少用戶煩惱。雖然這個漏洞發動條件較高，對操作並沒有太大影響，但已構成不便，估計蘋果未來會著手解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/15/ios-11-2-1-emoji-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2Fios-11-2-1-emoji-bug%2F&d=2rNSGEhzOSfKEq7qg3fthFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b877ff7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/12/15/ios-11-2-1-emoji-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"62c48f6d101a19ea70fcb35af0a6ef17fe8ed128","tid":500168,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f01799831861c2c127683ec3172b1f1f2986f70a","tid":500168,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4ffc726cfc408334d8ec759047d7e1dd33c29f","tid":500168,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"無人理你呀腦魔"},{"pid":"f42ed4d758f81340d57c2c5c4be121fe73eef4a0","tid":500168,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"但已構成不便，估計蘋果未來會著手解決<br />\n但已構成不便，估計蘋果未來會著手解決<br />\n但已構成不便，估計蘋果未來會著手解決<br />\n但已構成不便，估計蘋果未來會著手解決"},{"p